cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image captioning. It also involves Natural Language Processing (NLP) as it generates captions for images, which suggests it could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for semi-supervised learning suggests it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models, which could place it in the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the use of a dataset (MS COCO) suggests it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
